ollow_qt__gt_http_dd_//pryme8.github.io/TERIABLE/infinity.html_lt_/a_gt__lt_br /_gt__lt_br /_gt_\n\tHonestly the script to infinity is more relevant for you guys then the basic Teriable_co_ the mesh manipulation is not the hard part and nore is spawning the new zones the hard part would be the LOD stack if you wanted to incorporate that.  Mainly because you would not want to add lets say 3 meshs onto the draw stack with each spawn_co_ but would want to trickle them to it in essence_co_ I know that sound crazy... but maybe Ill do a LOD example here soon too.  There is just so much on my plate at the moment with me looking for a new major contract now and having to learn Drupal (uhg) for one of my clients.\n_lt_/p_gt_\n\n\n\t\t\t\n\t\t_lt_/div_gt_\n\n\t\t_lt_div class_eq__qt_ipsI_qt__gt__lt_/div_gt__lt_/div_gt_"}]